channel.title: Comments on: xCellerate2008 – Bringing Silicon Valley to Ireland event

item.title: By: Conor O'Neill
item.dc:creator: Conor O'Neill
item.description: Looks like a great lineup. I've signed up. Tip for those using Google Checkout for the first time (like me). Postcode=1 seems to be the only thing that works. The classic C1, C0001, NA or 90210 all fail.
